data.description: New opportunity for a home that has it all awaits! This home is presented beautifully in a cul de sac and walking distance to the elementary school. Offering OWNED solar, a great floor plan with 3 bedrooms, an office, 2 living areas and a low maintenance backyard with a pool/spa and outdoor seating!  The master bedroom is very large with an attached nook/room.  The kitchen was recently updated as well with new backsplash, counters, a built in seating.  Come take advantage today!
